Tron: Legacy is the soundtrack album for the 2010 film Tron: Legacy composed by French duo Daft Punk. The album was released on December 6, 2010. It is the first film score released by Daft Punk.  <a href="
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tron:_Legacy_(soundtrack)" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
